{"tid":2089640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蓬佩奧指《港區國安法》有條文冒犯所有國家","createTime":"2020-07-01T18:55:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T05:55:30.000Z","uid":66324,"like":287,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"1e195731529554a7b79a2e874fb49fea1786c7b2","tid":2089640,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T18:55:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535288-20200702.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535288-20200702.htm&d=Ia4lQUE8yf8cF0bf%2B23B9R1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=002416c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535288-20200702.htm&h=69550f2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535288-20200702.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧在華盛頓形容，《港區國安法》第三十八條，是對所有國家的冒犯。第三十八條列明，不具有香港特區永久性居民身份的人在香港特區以外針對香港特區實施本法規定的犯罪的，適用本法。"},{"pid":"c128c4905a6b1cfab940a559c6ae4acf76ac4c6b","tid":2089640,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T19:47:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd230ba656997d5192a1ca47c420547b4db6f53a","tid":2089640,"uid":38516,"like":78,"dislike":2,"score":76,"citedBy":12,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T19:51:38.000Z","msg":"支那好快會收返呢句當無事"},{"pid":"8860f0ae549ef765fa39836cd84e720d3eaf8ff0","tid":2089640,"uid":186079,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"1e195731529554a7b79a2e874fb49fea1786c7b2","tid":2089640,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T18:55:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535288-20200702.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535288-20200702.htm&d=Ia4lQUE8yf8cF0bf%2